{"word":"τυμβεύω","slug":"τυμβεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τυμβεύω</b></el> <el>(τυμβεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:τύμβος'><el>τύμβος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to bury, entomb</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>χοὰς τυμβεῦσαί τινι</el> <i>to pour</i> libations <i>on</i> one's <i>grave</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to dwell entombed</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}